{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Getting Started with OUDS","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png"}],"modules":[{"name":"Welcome to Orange Unified Design System"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to add the package as dependency, import libraries and use theme and components for your apps."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","type":"heading","text":"Integrate OUDS","level":2},{"anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager","type":"heading","text":"Use Swift Package Manager","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to add the iOS library of "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}]},{"type":"text","text":", you need to add our "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"type":"text","text":" into your project."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To do that, add a new "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"package dependency"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to your "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode"}]},{"type":"text","text":" project by refering to it by "},{"code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You are free to choose whether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0"}]},{"type":"text","text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0-rc3"}]},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","type":"heading","text":"Import the librairies you need","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"type":"text","text":" products."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Tip","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets."}]}],"style":"tip","type":"aside"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeCompact \/\/ To use the Orange Compact theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"]},{"anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","type":"heading","text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","level":3},{"name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and useless constants."}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Import the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" product which suits your needs:","type":"text"}]},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Umbrella"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUI"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above and all themes","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes","type":"text"}]}]]]},{"anchor":"Chose-your-theme","type":"heading","text":"Chose your theme","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}]},{"type":"text","text":" framework provides today four themes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Theme"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Compact"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sosh"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For Sosh products","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Wireframe"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles","type":"text"}]}]]]},{"anchor":"Apply-a-theme","type":"heading","text":"Apply a theme","level":3},{"numberOfColumns":2,"type":"row","columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You will need to use for your application root view the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" also.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"]}],"size":1}]},{"numberOfColumns":2,"type":"row","columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"]}],"size":1}]},{"name":"Tip","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"style":"tip","type":"aside"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Trick-for-Xcode-Preview","level":3,"text":"Trick for Xcode Preview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you use Xcode "},{"code":"#Preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks, you will have to be sure the theme is instanciated and injected through the "},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because it is not possible today to override the legit "},{"code":"#Preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" block, you can instead use some of our utilities to wrap your content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"inside the "},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" automatically. These utilities come with the themes modules. Without them you may face errors about undefined theme."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Apply Orange theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangePreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Orange Compact theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangeCompactPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Sosh theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .soshPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Wireframe theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .wireframePreview()","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules"],"title":"Essentials","anchor":"Essentials"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"ic_module_intro.png":{"identifier":"ic_module_intro.png","type":"image","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_module_intro.png"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Modules":{"kind":"article","images":[{"identifier":"ic_module_intro.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_module_intro.png","type":"card"}],"title":"Modules","role":"article","abstract":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"module","type":"text"}]},{"text":" can be seen as a set of features and components to fill a need.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/modules","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Themes":{"kind":"article","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_intro.png"},{"identifier":"ic_theme_intro.png","type":"card"}],"title":"Themes","role":"article","abstract":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Themes"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" are applications of specific values for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"components tokens","type":"text"}]},{"text":" and dimensionsemantic tokens_ using in the end ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"raw tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}]},{"text":" contains any relevant tokens which can be used for components rendering.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"theme","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" can use its own assets like fonts and icons."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/themes","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Tokens":{"kind":"article","images":[{"identifier":"ic_design_token_intro.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_design_token_intro.png","type":"card"}],"title":"Tokens","role":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Design tokens represent the small, repeated design decisions that make up a design system’s visual style. Tokens wrap hard-coded static values, such as hexadecimal codes for color, with self-explanatory names. They are used to define the look and feel and the style of everything. They are exposed through the themes and can be used as they are.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/tokens","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Components":{"abstract":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Components","type":"text"}]},{"text":" are the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"text":" objects you can add in the views of your apps, like buttons, links, cards etc.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"Components","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/components","